ddb
=========
Darbot DataBase (ddb) in an agent managed database (amdb) built with a scalable graph 
database system for agents to reason, orchestrate, create, manage, query, etc. from connected data efficiently. Native graphs, an integrated search engine, 
with configurable schemas and JSON support, via a single query language.

What's New in ddb
------------------------

ddb extends ddb with:
- Full Prisma Support
- Arm64 Architecture Support  
- Enhanced Docker Support
- Complete FastAPI Integration

Getting Started with ddb
------------------------------

Quick Start with Docker (Arm64 supported):

    docker run -e ddb_ROOT_PASSWORD=test123 -p 8529:8529 -d ddb

Then point your browser to http://127.0.0.1:8529/

ddb Repository: https://github.com/dayour/ddb
Issues: https://github.com/dayour/ddb/issues

Upstream ddb Resources:
- Documentation: https://docs.ddb.com/
